{"tid":686354,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"劉曉波雕塑擺放銅鑼灣","createTime":"2018-06-01T07:39:15.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-01T07:52:22.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"3bed439e93806b633393ad87290371c7a0e98c91","tid":686354,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T07:39:15.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180601/20407898\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180601%2F20407898&d=JnLVKeEM%2FheA9YYMrJKQb%2F%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=f3463500\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180601%2F20407898&h=11c8447e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180601/20407898</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年06月01日 <br />\n<br />\n劉曉波雕塑擺放銅鑼灣<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180601/large/01la7p41.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180601%2Flarge%2F01la7p41.jpg&h=e36d679f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】六四集會舉行在即，支聯會昨在銅鑼灣時代廣場外，擺放已故中國異見分子、2010年諾貝爾和平獎得主劉曉波的雕塑（圖）。<br />\n<br />\n支聯會十多名成員聯同民主派議員毛孟靜及張超雄，高叫「結束中共專政」等口號，並收集市民簽名，要求中共釋放被軟禁的劉曉波遺孀劉霞及其他政治犯。支聯會主席何俊仁希望藉雕塑延續劉的堅守精神及價值。支聯會明日會聯同其他團體，由西區警署遊行往中聯辦，要求釋放因悼念六四而被捕的人。<br />\n<br />\n許頌明攝   <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n支青組城大生堅持爭取平反「中港民主息息相關」<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n兩團體申維園旁集會「挑機」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n支青組城大生堅持爭取平反「中港民主息息相關」<br />\n<br />\n兩團體申維園旁集會「挑機」<br />\n<br />\n英密件揭中共　用衞星偷外媒六四片作政治宣傳兼助緝捕民運人士"},{"pid":"5d5fdb8f4f63b1c17a7a328b3f45e791f740a79b","tid":686354,"uid":2419,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T07:43:14.000Z","msg":"嘩 中共肯定嚇到標屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3ff3e8d11e2e623895b4c7dfaedf1ff992e51db","tid":686354,"uid":155818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T07:44:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b375dad060061acae6667eacb3523063f79847b5","tid":686354,"uid":184679,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T07:45:31.000Z","msg":"行為藝術<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a8caec957618b999b6253448531ea38132a89bb","tid":686354,"uid":117602,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5d5fdb8f4f63b1c17a7a328b3f45e791f740a79b","tid":686354,"uid":2419,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T07:43:14.000Z","msg":"嘩 中共肯定嚇到標屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T07:47:56.000Z","msg":"有咁多簽名，眾怒難犯 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d940d328eef2808b8d1cd92bab25ec53884a0e0","tid":686354,"uid":120070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T07:48:53.000Z","msg":"挑機 ？ 今次覺得會被清"},{"pid":"059913b48938ab5af566764023989341919e45ad","tid":686354,"uid":76216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T07:49:37.000Z","msg":"唔得啦 唔得啦<br />\n咁搞一定解放軍入城<br />\n中共一定嬲到震<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7164d0830aaa05d0273825ec4f0156ee617d8c09","tid":686354,"uid":86893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0a8caec957618b999b6253448531ea38132a89bb","tid":686354,"uid":117602,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5d5fdb8f4f63b1c17a7a328b3f45e791f740a79b","tid":686354,"uid":2419,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T07:43:14.000Z","msg":"嘩 中共肯定嚇到標屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T07:47:56.000Z","msg":"有咁